  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "sXfM5LW5K7GscsuPa0CJSFwart8=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:36.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# helper functions\n\nHelper functions that live outside reducers but are critical to editor behavior \u2014 pricing calculations, billing breakdowns, cross-model data mapping, and formatting utilities.\n\n## Pricing Calculation (Service Offering)\n- [[getUserSelectionPriceBreakdown is the core pricing calculation engine]] \u2014 the master pricing function in service-offering/src/utils.ts\n- [[pricing-utils provides editor-level formatting and tier price calculations]] \u2014 formatPrice, calculateTierRecurringPrice, calculateEffectiveSetupPrice, detectMajorityCycle\n\n## Billing Calculation (Subscription Instance)\n- [[billing-utils computes subscription billing breakdowns and metric overages]] \u2014 computeBillingBreakdown, formatCurrency, computeMetricOverage\n\n## Cross-Model Bridges\n- [[mapOfferingToSubscription transforms service offering state into subscription initialization]] \u2014 converts offering final config \u2192 subscription init input\n\n## Dependency Graph\n\n```\nservice-offering/src/utils.ts\n  \u2514\u2500 getUserSelectionPriceBreakdown \u2192 TheMatrix.tsx\n\neditors/service-offering-editor/components/pricing-utils.ts\n  \u251c\u2500 re-exports BILLING_CYCLE_MONTHS from model\n  \u2514\u2500 formatPrice, calculateTierRecurringPrice \u2192 ServiceCatalog, TierDefinition, TheMatrix\n\neditors/service-offering-editor/components/resolve-configuration.ts\n  \u2514\u2500 resolveConfiguration \u2192 TheMatrix.tsx (converts PriceBreakdown \u2192 SetFinalConfigurationInput)\n\neditors/subscription-instance-editor/components/billing-utils.ts\n  \u2514\u2500 computeBillingBreakdown \u2192 BillingPanel.tsx\n\neditors/subscription-instance-editor/components/mapOfferingToSubscription.ts\n  \u2514\u2500 mapOfferingToSubscription \u2192 ImportServiceConfigButton.tsx\n```\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[index]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:36.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:36.000Z"
    }
  },
